  "solution": "**Step 1: Define Key Variables**<br>CF1 = $80,000, CF2 = $120,000, r = 0.06. <br> **Step 2: Calculate Present Value**<br>PV = CF1/(1 + r)^1 + CF2/(1 + r)^2 = $80,000/(1.06) + $120,000/(1.06^2) = $188,679."
